{"tid":1261163,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"[集思廣益] 香港烈士紀念旗","createTime":"2019-06-27T06:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T13:03:26.000Z","uid":2386,"like":78,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a595a65d3c6b77a5e4ee9cbf05a76cae50136903","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"利申：唔識design，但好想設計支旗去紀念烈士<br />\n所以跟住旗幟設計原則嗰五項，畫咗幅烈士紀念旗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G62MAPf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG62MAPf.png&h=5bababa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n意念：<br />\n<br />\n首先完全放棄洋紫荊圖案，用烈士做主體以紀念烈士嘅犧牲<br />\n用色上，藍黃係舊香港旗嘅主色，唔係戀殖，只為喚起大家當年美好香港嘅情感<br />\n<br />\n藍 = 自由<br />\n黃 = 希望 + 雨革及烈士雨褸嘅代表顏色<br />\n<br />\n黃色圖形 = <br />\n1. 烈士背影嘅幾何化 (因為一定要簡單，細路都記得同識畫)<br />\n2. 上面菱形可以睇成搭喺烈士膊頭上嘅雨傘<br />\n3. 下面梯形除咗可以睇成烈士嘅身，亦可以睇成一條有希望嘅路<br />\n<br />\n各位睇下好唔好，或者有咩改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb78f6a0f4bb05ddf2937972038e8228478b2e7","tid":1261163,"uid":263943,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"藍色比建制用到爛有啲尷尬，諗緊黑底會唔會好啲"},{"pid":"6e6986c9f45ff0c2dd93018167904d1d92b76939","tid":1261163,"uid":46688,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7507b86f0e6a8266aaa38b89cf12515e00d93325","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6eb78f6a0f4bb05ddf2937972038e8228478b2e7","tid":1261163,"uid":263943,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"藍色比建制用到爛有啲尷尬，諗緊黑底會唔會好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"黑底太沉，感覺太絕望，唔太啱做旗<br />\n好似暫時未見過有國旗、市旗係黑底?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e3bc64da38f5771cad21510e0444d26292e21f","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"旗幟學作為一門學科，也在推廣這些旗幟設計原則。例如被北美旗幟學協會認可的、Ted Kaye提出的五大「Good Flag, Bad Flag」原則：<br />\n<br />\n簡單：旗幟圖案必須簡單到一個孩子能根據記憶畫出來；<br />\n有意義：旗幟的圖案、色彩、圖像應當有其含義；<br />\n用2-3種基本色：使得旗幟有良好的對比度；<br />\n沒有文字或圖章：不要使用文字和印章；<br />\n獨一無二：避免與其它旗幟相同，但可通過使用相似圖案或顏色以顯示與其的聯繫。"},{"pid":"a9568bdda85a8952a65dc08ef21e3960e5ffbcf7","tid":1261163,"uid":259711,"like":22,"dislike":12,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"要整就整支國旗出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個整嘅但係我覺得幾好<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6air2C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6air2C.png&h=799f8163&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64kKnAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64kKnAY.png&h=5cf0a9ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0662ee0ffb016a0fa4233dddaa4d0f4920d41b8f","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9568bdda85a8952a65dc08ef21e3960e5ffbcf7","tid":1261163,"uid":259711,"like":22,"dislike":12,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"要整就整支國旗出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個整嘅但係我覺得幾好<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6air2C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6air2C.png&h=799f8163&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64kKnAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64kKnAY.png&h=5cf0a9ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:20:46.000Z","msg":"呢支都好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我呢支主題就紀念烈士多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ec9431202ed0f96445ab22284ccbc4644fccec","tid":1261163,"uid":28759,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a9568bdda85a8952a65dc08ef21e3960e5ffbcf7","tid":1261163,"uid":259711,"like":22,"dislike":12,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"要整就整支國旗出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個整嘅但係我覺得幾好<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6air2C.p