952a65dc08ef21e3960e5ffbcf7","tid":1261163,"uid":259711,"like":22,"dislike":12,"score":10,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:19:03.000Z","msg":"要整就整支國旗出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個整嘅但係我覺得幾好<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m6air2C.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm6air2C.png&h=799f8163&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64kKnAY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64kKnAY.png&h=5cf0a9ba&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T11:31:22.000Z","msg":"呢支真係靚"},{"pid":"c7f0d33bb96a950e3f293b1e063161c27f173318","tid":1261163,"uid":145111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"點解隻黃...好似有啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4ebba7acfee847635849ebaa74936fb03c36879","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7f0d33bb96a950e3f293b1e063161c27f173318","tid":1261163,"uid":145111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T12:02:29.000Z","msg":"點解隻黃...好似有啲怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"本身唔想太鮮色所以淡啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鮮啲好?"},{"pid":"1e54f270dc443256b1f41098b9fb45c477abfb66","tid":1261163,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T15:39:57.000Z","msg":"依隻藍色  <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97bc9df48f64c31c887ba60f0a83c3bd66a7e878","tid":1261163,"uid":25327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7507b86f0e6a8266aaa38b89cf12515e00d93325","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6eb78f6a0f4bb05ddf2937972038e8228478b2e7","tid":1261163,"uid":263943,"like":5,"dislike":17,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:12:52.000Z","msg":"藍色比建制用到爛有啲尷尬，諗緊黑底會唔會好啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T06:15:18.000Z","msg":"黑底太沉，感覺太絕望，唔太啱做旗<br />\n好似暫時未見過有國旗、市旗係黑底?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T19:18:24.000Z","msg":"絕望中帶點希望"},{"pid":"8d42810889ed0404c721a71588d6667d7747cf2f","tid":1261163,"uid":189453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T20:59:32.000Z","msg":"隻藍白花旗設計得幾靚<br />\n<br />\nbtw如果真係要升旗 又驚比人話係港獨       最多係隔離升埋 支國 旗囉"},{"pid":"8bcb5398c6d8bc6dc0c64b611332635640e80fd2","tid":1261163,"uid":8000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T21:24:01.000Z","msg":"好多人仲未接受到港獨<br />\n但支藍白旗真心靚<br />\n<br />\nbtw樓主個支 黃色想你盡量跟返烈士隻黃<br />\n佢隻黃係有種活力係度<br />\n有種對生命奮鬥既感覺<br />\n個底試下跟返海軍藍<br />\n再試下出個幾何圖 拉長或拉闊 個比例會唔會好怪<br />\n整完up上黎睇下  <br />\n應該唔難<br />\nthanks"},{"pid":"59114888b14df5f1e902e2d26b30de7e420c9a40","tid":1261163,"uid":32063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:01:53.000Z","msg":"推 我地需要依樣野多過香港旗<br />\n最少我地可以話依支係記念佢既旗<br />\n可進可退<br />\n其他我覺得太hardcore香港人一時間好難接受<br />\n<br />\n雖然我建議係上黃下黑<br />\n我地就好似由義士引導<br />\n香港人捨棄黑暗向希望前進咁"},{"pid":"a26bfbfb8e6638074f2aee52551ace4f9fb01b4a","tid":1261163,"uid":32063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"始終唔明點解大家咁執著藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0180addfa09005620e0e03372e59fc9ff99e2c","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:08:07.000Z","msg":"Ver.2<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WagU144.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWagU144.png&h=19c80ffe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽完大意見，主要係顏色問題<br />\n我用返香港旗嘅藍同黃去做主色，的確係靚啲<br />\n<br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6777037f307dba55472409f348f7d3c3f19bc0fe","tid":1261163,"uid":2386,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a26bfbfb8e6638074f2aee52551ace4f9fb01b4a","tid":1261163,"uid":32063,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"始終唔明點解大家咁執著藍色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T10:11:50.000Z","msg":"情意結<br />\n同紅色對立<br />\n靚<br />\n多數代表自由<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}